headline: 4 Gas Distribution Stocks to Accumulate in a Thriving Industry
summary: Ongoing increases in natural gas export volumes and regular investment in pipelines are driving the Zacks Gas Distribution industry's near-term prospects. Utilities with stable infrastructure like ATO, SWX, NJR and CPK are well-poised to gain.
